27F6DBFD.Line7.789BF: I am plagued by a demon and the memories she brings forth. How do I purge them?

6F245388.Line11.789BF: Brothers and sisters of the swamp, I thank you for heeding my call.

915323B5.Line5.F53E7: No, no, no. This is a question of will. You must wrestle these thoughts into submission. Lock them away in a place from which they will never return.

E266EDC2.Line16.1086F0: It is very simple. You’ve let your mind wander -- let the memories consume you. Put your idle hands at work, commit to your craft, and soon you will forget all about this nonsense.
